%% Error Handling Flow Diagram
flowchart TD
    A[Normal Operation] --> B{Error Occurs?}
    
    B -->|Ollama Connection Failed| C["Display: \"Could not connect to Ollama.\nPlease ensure it's running:\n  ollama serve\""]
    B -->|MCP Server Connection Failed| D["Display: \"Cannot connect to MCP server.\nCommand: uv run python -m weather_mcp.main\nWorking directory: /path/to/project\""]
    B -->|API Key Missing| E["Display: \"OpenWeatherMap API key not found.\nPlease set OPENWEATHERMAP_API_KEY in .env\""]
    B -->|Invalid City| F["Display: \"City 'InvalidCity123' not found.\nPlease check the spelling.\""]
    B -->|API Rate Limit| G["Display: \"API rate limit exceeded.\nPlease try again later.\""]
    B -->|LLM Timeout| H["Display: \"Ollama request timed out.\nThe model might be too large.\""]
    B -->|Tool Call Parse Error| I[Continue with text-only response]
    B -->|Max Iterations| J["Display: \"Couldn't complete request\nafter multiple attempts.\""]
    
    C --> K[Exit with error]
    D --> K
    E --> K
    F --> L[Continue conversation]
    G --> L
    H --> L
    I --> L
    J --> L
    
    K --> M[System Failure]
    L --> N[Graceful Degradation]